    <div class="help-section">
        <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
        
        <h3>No Speech Output:</h3>
        <div class="troubleshooting-box">
            <p><strong>Problem:</strong> TTS is enabled but no sound</p>
            <p><strong>Solutions:</strong></p>
            <ol>
                <li>Check system volume is not muted</li>
                <li>Verify TTS is enabled in Settings ? Accessibility</li>
                <li>Try a different browser (Chrome/Edge recommended)</li>
                <li>Check browser console for errors (F12)</li>
                <li>Reload the page</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <h3>Speech Too Fast/Slow:</h3>
        <div class="troubleshooting-box">
            <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Can't understand or speech is too slow</p>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Adjust speech rate in Settings ? Accessibility (0.5x - 2.0x)</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Wrong Voice/Accent:</h3>
        <div class="troubleshooting-box">
            <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Voice sounds unusual or wrong language</p>
            <p><strong>Reason:</strong> Browser uses system default voice</p>
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Windows:</strong> Settings ? Time & Language ? Speech</li>
                <li><strong>Mac:</strong> System Preferences ? Accessibility ? Speech</li>
                <li><strong>Linux:</strong> Depends on distribution</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
        <h2>Accessibility Benefits</h2>
        <div class="alert alert-info">
            <i class="fas fa-universal-access"></i>
            <strong>Who Benefits:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Users with visual impairments</li>
                <li>Users with reading difficulties</li>
                <li>Users who prefer audio feedback</li>
                <li>Multitasking users (hands-free operation)</li>
                <li>Users learning to use the application</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
        <h2>Privacy & Security</h2>
        <div class="alert alert-success">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            <strong>Your Data is Safe:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>All speech processing happens in your browser</li>
                <li>No audio recorded or stored</li>
                <li>No data sent to external servers</li>
                <li>Completely offline capable</li>
                <li>No API keys or accounts required</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
        <h2>Technical Details</h2>
        <table class="table">
            <tr>
                <th>Technology</th>
                <td>Web Speech API (Browser Built-in)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Cost</th>
                <td>FREE (No API fees or limits)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Setup Time</th>
                <td>0 minutes (Works immediately)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Languages</th>
                <td>Depends on system voices</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Offline</th>
                <td>Yes (Uses system voices)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Customizable</th>
                <td>Speed control (0.5x - 2.0x)</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
        <h2>Tips & Best Practices</h2>
        <div class="tip-box">
            <h3>?? Pro Tips:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Start with normal speed (1.0x) and adjust as needed</li>
                <li>Use headphones in quiet environments for better experience</li>
                <li>Combine with screen reader for full accessibility</li>
                <li>Test with different browsers to find best voice</li>
                <li>Install additional system voices for more options</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-navigation">
        <a href="/help/accessibility" class="btn btn-outline">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Accessibility
        </a>
        <a href="/help" class="btn btn-secondary">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Back to Help
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

